00:32:01,766 --> 00:32:04,600
I thought you wouldn't be,
since you're an introvert.

582
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:08,520
Um... It's because my performance
hasn't been good lately,

583
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:11,500
so I thought this TV show
might be my chance.

