638
00:35:13,300 --> 00:35:15,720
He was just so loose,
smiling like that...

639
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:16,853
Um... Yoon-seo?

640
00:35:16,933 --> 00:35:18,553
Right? He's so mean, right?

641
00:35:18,633 --> 00:35:20,086
You think so too, right?

