something wasn't right.

651
00:35:40,166 --> 00:35:42,753
Still, I told myself
no way, but...

652
00:35:42,833 --> 00:35:45,286
You know, you acting like this
is a bit...

653
00:35:45,366 --> 00:35:47,853
Is a bit, what?

654
00:35:47,933 --> 00:35:49,786
It's like you're jealous.

655
00:35:49,866 --> 00:35:50,866
What?

656
00:35:51,733 --> 00:35:52,766
Jealous?

657
00:35:57,600 --> 00:35:58,953
Did I fall for him?

658
00:35:59,033 --> 00:36:00,366
Am I jealous?

659
00:36:01,266 --> 00:36:03,633
Why on earth would he
ever think that?

660
00:36:04,966 --> 00:36:06,220
This is not good.
I should watch myself,

661
00:36:06,300 --> 00:36:07,786
