00:36:53,033 --> 00:36:55,620
But you should.
You're his secretary.

680
00:36:55,700 --> 00:36:56,700
Huh?

681
00:36:57,933 --> 00:37:01,386
Oh, that's right.

682
00:37:01,466 --> 00:37:04,666
He said he'll be with a client
so he's coming late today.

683
00:37:05,700 --> 00:37:06,700
