684
00:37:09,633 --> 00:37:11,820
Good morning to our viewers.

685
00:37:11,900 --> 00:37:14,120
I'm Han Seok-gyu, your host of
Morning Korea.

686
00:37:14,200 --> 00:37:17,086
Huh? I don't see Mr. Choi.

687
00:37:17,166 --> 00:37:20,120
You're right. Where did he go?

688
00:37:20,200 --> 00:37:21,353
Here I am!

689
00:37:21,433 --> 00:37:22,920
...on the show today.

690
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:23,920
Hello.

691
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:25,300
What happened?

692
00:37:26,033 --> 00:37:27,320
Aren't you supposed to be
on that show?

693
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:29,220
Mr. Yeon received
a call this morning,

