an advocate of the
4th Industrial Revolution,

715
00:38:33,500 --> 00:38:35,853
has defined it as
a technological revolution

716
00:38:35,933 --> 00:38:37,853
where the physical, digital, and
biological spheres

717
00:38:37,933 --> 00:38:40,186
from the 3rd Industrial Revolution

718
00:38:40,266 --> 00:38:42,586
