00:39:04,533 --> 00:39:06,186
That's all he said?

729
00:39:06,266 --> 00:39:08,833
He's embarrassing Always.

730
00:39:13,366 --> 00:39:14,986
This is all because of you, Mom.

731
00:39:15,066 --> 00:39:17,286
